{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-tsx","path":"/slack_trello_alert/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<blockquote>\n<p>좋은 글감을 획득했다! 두고두고 사용될 것 같으니 기록함</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"1-slack-설정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-slack-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"1 slack 설정 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. Slack 설정</h2>\n<h3 id=\"1-workspace\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-workspace\" aria-label=\"1 workspace permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. workspace</h3>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">workspace</code> 가 필요하다. 이미 있으면 그거 사용하고 없으면 만드세유 (<code class=\"language-text\">test</code> 라는 이름으로 만들었다.)</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>이 방법은 slack 에서 <code class=\"language-text\">trello app</code>을 설치하지 않고, trello를 통해서 설치합니다! 하지만 이미 <code class=\"language-text\">app</code>이 설치되어 있더라도 방법은 동일했던 것 같습니다. (절차가 하나 줄어들 뿐)</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"2-trello와-연결할-channel\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-trello%EC%99%80-%EC%97%B0%EA%B2%B0%ED%95%A0-channel\" aria-label=\"2 trello와 연결할 channel permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. trello와 연결할 channel</h3>\n<img width=\"200\" alt=\"&#x1109;&#x1173;&#x110F;&#x1173;&#x1105;&#x1175;&#x11AB;&#x1109;&#x1163;&#x11BA; 2020-07-01 &#x110B;&#x1169;&#x110C;&#x1165;&#x11AB; 2 09 20\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/37680108/86156128-6d0b9c80-bb40-11ea-89fe-6eb214e9679c.png\">\n<p>trello와 연결할 channel을 만들어 두었다. (여기선 <code class=\"language-text\">#trello</code>)</p>\n<h2 id=\"2-trello-설정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-trello-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"2 trello 설정 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. Trello 설정</h2>\n<h3 id=\"1-board-생성\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-board-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1\" aria-label=\"1 board 생성 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. board 생성</h3>\n<p>스샷 생략.</p>\n<h3 id=\"2-power-up에-slack-추가\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-power-up%EC%97%90-slack-%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80\" aria-label=\"2 power up에 slack 추가 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. Power-up에 Slack 추가</h3>\n<p><strong>(1)</strong> board에 들어가면 우측에 <code class=\"language-text\">Show Menu</code> 가 있다. 클릭!</p>\n<img width=\"200\" alt=\"&#x1109;&#x1173;&#x110F;&#x1173;&#x1105;&#x1175;&#x11AB;&#x1109;&#x1163;&#x11BA; 2020-07-01 &#x110B;&#x1169;&#x110C;&#x1165;&#x11AB; 1 39 04\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/37680108/86156498-00dd6880-bb41-11ea-997c-cf57432b3de5.png\">\n<p><strong>(2)</strong> <code class=\"language-text\">Add Power-up</code> 클릭!</p>\n<img width=\"300\" alt=\"&#x1109;&#x1173;&#x110F;&#x1173;&#x1105;&#x1175;&#x11AB;&#x1109;&#x1163;&#x11BA; 2020-07-01 &#x110B;&#x1169;&#x110C;&#x1165;&#x11AB; 1 39 16\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/37680108/86156540-15b9fc00-bb41-11ea-98b5-b26dd02ad87c.png\">\n<p><strong>(3)</strong> <code class=\"language-text\">slack 추가</code>하슈</p>\n<img width=\"500\" alt=\"&#x1109;&#x1173;&#x110F;&#x1173;&#x1105;&#x1175;&#x11AB;&#x1109;&#x1163;&#x11BA; 2020-07-01 &#x110B;&#x1169;&#x110C;&#x1165;&#x11AB; 1 40 48\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/37680108/86156615-32563400-bb41-11ea-80b8-227970b866ba.png\">\n<p><strong>(4)</strong> 그러면 이렇게 바뀌는데, 무료라서 제한이 있나봅니다. <code class=\"language-text\">Settings</code> 클릭! 후 <code class=\"language-text\">Edit Power-up Settings</code> 클릭!</p>\n<img width=\"500\" alt=\"&#x1109;&#x1173;&#x110F;&#x1173;&#x1105;&#x1175;&#x11AB;&#x1109;&#x1163;&#x11BA; 2020-07-01 &#x110B;&#x1169;&#x110C;&#x1165;&#x11AB; 1 41 27\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/37680108/86156681-4e59d580-bb41-11ea-85a2-b7bf7598513d.png\">\n<img width=\"300\" alt=\"&#x1109;&#x1173;&#x110F;&#x1173;&#x1105;&#x1175;&#x11AB;&#x1109;&#x1163;&#x11BA; 2020-07-01 &#x110B;&#x1169;&#x110C;&#x1165;&#x11AB; 1 42 00\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/37680108/86156798-76e1cf80-bb41-11ea-94d7-fa5b546507b9.png\">\n<h3 id=\"3-power-up-settings\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-power-up-settings\" aria-label=\"3 power up settings permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. Power-Up Settings</h3>\n<p><strong>(1)</strong> <code class=\"language-text\">Add Slack Alert</code> 클릭해 줍니다</p>\n<img width=\"500\" alt=\"&#x1109;&#x1173;&#x110F;&#x1173;&#x1105;&#x1175;&#x11AB;&#x1109;&#x1163;&#x11BA; 2020-07-01 &#x110B;&#x1169;&#x110C;&#x1165;&#x11AB; 1 42 36\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/37680108/86157133-e9eb4600-bb41-11ea-930a-7cfad5ef3fb7.png\">\n<p><strong>(2)</strong> 다음과 같이 뜨는데, Slack team에서 <strong>우측 버튼</strong>을 눌러 원하는 team이 있으면 선택합니다.(<em>선택했으면 3-(2)번으로 이동</em>) 없으면 <code class=\"language-text\">Add new Slack team</code>을 클릭합니다. (<em>(3)으로 이동</em>)</p>\n<img width=\"500\" alt=\"&#x1109;&#x1173;&#x110F;&#x1173;&#x1105;&#x1175;&#x11AB;&#x1109;&#x1163;&#x11BA; 2020-07-01 &#x110B;&#x1169;&#x110C;&#x1165;&#x11AB; 1 44 33\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/37680108/86157186-fbcce900-bb41-11ea-84bd-1457064d7cfd.png\">\n<p><strong>(3)</strong> 기본적으로 새로 만든 <strong>workspace가 선택</strong>되어 있습니다. 그렇지 않다면 클릭해서 변경해 주세요(사진참고) workspace 확인했으면 <code class=\"language-text\">Allow</code> 클릭!</p>\n<img width=\"500\" alt=\"&#x1109;&#x1173;&#x110F;&#x1173;&#x1105;&#x1175;&#x11AB;&#x1109;&#x1163;&#x11BA; 2020-07-01 &#x110B;&#x1169;&#x110C;&#x1165;&#x11AB; 1 45 40\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/37680108/86157368-42bade80-bb42-11ea-9c81-03bae9a59ef2.png\">\n<p><strong>(4)</strong> 이런 창이 뜹니다. (대충 slack에 trello설치를 위한 계정 확인) <code class=\"language-text\">Link Accounts</code> 해줍시다</p>\n<img width=\"400\" alt=\"&#x1109;&#x1173;&#x110F;&#x1173;&#x1105;&#x1175;&#x11AB;&#x1109;&#x1163;&#x11BA; 2020-07-01 &#x110B;&#x1169;&#x110C;&#x1165;&#x11AB; 1 50 19\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/37680108/86157654-afce7400-bb42-11ea-9eab-17d067be6f26.png\">\n<p><strong>(5)</strong> 해당 이메일에 들어가면 Slack에게 메일이 와 있습니다!! (대충 <strong>Trello를 Slack에 깔았다</strong>는 뜻) 예의상 <code class=\"language-text\">Sign In</code> 한 번 눌러줍니다.</p>\n<img width=\"500\" alt=\"&#x1109;&#x1173;&#x110F;&#x1173;&#x1105;&#x1175;&#x11AB;&#x1109;&#x1163;&#x11BA; 2020-07-01 &#x110B;&#x1169;&#x110C;&#x1165;&#x11AB; 1 52 36\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/37680108/86157940-0b98fd00-bb43-11ea-9cb7-36b4ebae3e53.png\">\n<p><strong>(6)</strong> <strong>Slack 에 들어가</strong>서 <code class=\"language-text\">Apps</code> 를 클릭하면 다음과 같이 Trello 가 설치되어 있다고 뜹니다.</p>\n<img width=\"200\" alt=\"&#x1109;&#x1173;&#x110F;&#x1173;&#x1105;&#x1175;&#x11AB;&#x1109;&#x1163;&#x11BA; 2020-07-01 &#x110B;&#x1169;&#x110C;&#x1165;&#x11AB; 1 54 36\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/37680108/86158086-40a54f80-bb43-11ea-91f1-27606752cbaf.png\">\n<img width=\"300\" alt=\"&#x1109;&#x1173;&#x110F;&#x1173;&#x1105;&#x1175;&#x11AB;&#x1109;&#x1163;&#x11BA; 2020-07-01 &#x110B;&#x1169;&#x110C;&#x1165;&#x11AB; 2 00 27\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/37680108/86158189-65012c00-bb43-11ea-8cb6-f646c6eb0a48.png\">\n<h2 id=\"3-본격적인-연동\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-%EB%B3%B8%EA%B2%A9%EC%A0%81%EC%9D%B8-%EC%97%B0%EB%8F%99\" aria-label=\"3 본격적인 연동 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. 본격적인 연동!</h2>\n<p><strong>(1)</strong> Trello로 돌아가서 이 페이지로 다시 갔다가 와 줍니다.</p>\n<img width=\"500\" alt=\"&#x1109;&#x1173;&#x110F;&#x1173;&#x1105;&#x1175;&#x11AB;&#x1109;&#x1163;&#x11BA; 2020-07-01 &#x110B;&#x1169;&#x110C;&#x1165;&#x11AB; 1 42 36\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/37680108/86157133-e9eb4600-bb41-11ea-930a-7cfad5ef3fb7.png\">\n<p><strong>(2)</strong> 짠 Slack team 에서 새로운 <strong>workspace가 선택</strong> 가능해졌어요💁‍♀️밑에 <strong>channel도 선택</strong>해줍시다! (아까 만든 <code class=\"language-text\">#trello</code>채널로 했음)</p>\n<img width=\"500\" alt=\"&#x1109;&#x1173;&#x110F;&#x1173;&#x1105;&#x1175;&#x11AB;&#x1109;&#x1163;&#x11BA; 2020-07-01 &#x110B;&#x1169;&#x110C;&#x1165;&#x11AB; 2 03 05\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/37680108/86158497-d214c180-bb43-11ea-8732-eab24be8080e.png\">\n<p><strong>(3)</strong> 알람을 설정합니다. 다 클릭하면 슬랙이 너무나 많은 양의 알람속에,,, 묻혀버립ㄴ,,,, 즉당히 필요한 것만 해줍니다,,,</p>\n<img width=\"500\" alt=\"&#x1109;&#x1173;&#x110F;&#x1173;&#x1105;&#x1175;&#x11AB;&#x1109;&#x1163;&#x11BA; 2020-07-01 &#x110B;&#x1169;&#x110C;&#x1165;&#x11AB; 2 04 10\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/37680108/86158626-05575080-bb44-11ea-9b2f-f7720a432390.png\">\n<p><strong>(4)</strong> <strong>던!!</strong> 맨 밑에 <code class=\"language-text\">Done</code> 클릭</p>\n<img width=\"154\" alt=\"&#x1109;&#x1173;&#x110F;&#x1173;&#x1105;&#x1175;&#x11AB;&#x1109;&#x1163;&#x11BA; 2020-07-01 &#x110B;&#x1169;&#x110C;&#x1165;&#x11AB; 2 04 17\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/37680108/86158723-29b32d00-bb44-11ea-9294-d1b121579313.png\">\n<h2 id=\"4-끝\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#4-%EB%81%9D\" aria-label=\"4 끝 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>4. 끝!</h2>\n<h3 id=\"1-trello-에-slack-alert가-추가된-모습\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-trello-%EC%97%90-slack-alert%EA%B0%80-%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80%EB%90%9C-%EB%AA%A8%EC%8A%B5\" aria-label=\"1 trello 에 slack alert가 추가된 모습 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h